<br>
And, for some reason that I can't quite articulate at the moment, saying that they are camping the ledge to acquire some loot dropped from a mob at the ledge does not equate to camping a mob for the component for one of the Epic quests.<br>
<br>
On the subject of reserving vs. stating intentions.  I was, actually, under the assumption that I was reserving CoM for at least a few hours that evening.  Being new to this board, I may have misunderstood how things work - I apologize if I did.  The first time I came here I saw CoM in the reservation summary, so I assumed it could be reserved.  I don't really care whether we call it an intention or a reservation - assuming a server of polite people, either should have the same result - CoM will be available at the time you reserved/intended it because either people are respecting your reservation or they are being polite and deciding to go elsewhere because a fellow EQer really needs to mob X.<br>
